Omolola Afolabi Sensational singer, Emilio has dropped his debut single titled Amaka featuring Wealth Kalifa. The single which will be released in April is already on airplay and enjoying rotation with top Disc Jockeys in Nigeria. Powered by RubiQube Ad Network, Amaka tug on your heartstrings as listeners are filled with nostalgia from the familiar bitter sweetness of hopeless young love. Speaking on the single, the duo told The Nation that Amaka was inspired by Emilio’s heartbreak which he described as “hellish”. “I had to resort to the studio for comfort during my ordeal, it was my only place of comfort during that period,” he said. Very autonomous by nature, one thing the duo has in common with most true artistes is how they express themselves and their life experience through art.